ALL NEW First Friday's at the Modern experience. Explore KAWS: WHERE THE END STARTS with extended, late-night hours and live music during First Friday's Delivered at the museum.

Shipping & Receiving Bar, the unique Near Southside music and night-life venue, teams up with the Modern to showcase premier local musicians set against the stunning background of the Museum's Grand Lobby from 6 to 11 pm. Invite friends to enjoy unique cocktail selections, and the opportunity to dine at the Modern by night. Cafe Modern offers a full menu in the dining room and lighter fare in the Grand Lobby until 9 pm.

This ticket includes gallery admission. A docent-led, 20-minute tour of the galleries is available at 6:30 pm. KAWS: WHERE THE END BEGINS is on view until 10 pm.
